      "retweeted_tweet_id": null,
      "text": "On Sunday, October 12, threatening messages were discovered graffitied on the USCIS building in Williston, Vermont. Vandalizers wrote, “kill yourselves,” “your not safe were coming,” and “die,” on our federal building.\n\nWe are not going to allow domestic terrorists to attack our law enforcement. DHS has already arrested dozens of Antifa-aligned left-wing violent extremists who have attacked law enforcement, murdered innocent civilians, and launched a wave of violent riots throughout the Unites States.\n\nSecretary Noem’s message to the rioters is clear: you will not stop us or slow us down.\n\nFederal law enforcement and the Williston Police Department are actively investigating these threats.",
